<item>
            <title>[SOLR-4289] Admin UI - JVM memory bar - dark grey &quot;used&quot; width is too small</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4289</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;See attached screenshot.  The red line shows approximately where the dark grey section &lt;b&gt;should&lt;/b&gt; end.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On the screenshot, the used memory is shown as 9.3% ... the width of the dark grey section (corresponding to used memory) should be 9.3% of the width of the full bar (max memory), but it appears that it is actually about 9.3% of the width of the mid-grey section (total memory).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am testing a potential patch right now, will attach it if it looks like it&apos;s working right.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
